
= ''Umwuga'' =
ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwandakazi]] wakoze umwuga w'umucuruzi ndetse n 'umunyapolitiki akaba ari na [[Minisitiri wa Siporo|Minisitiri wa sport]] <ref>https://minisports.gov.rw/index.php?id=30&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=1895&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=b7c82da2309f76e08e67b49c66685e64</ref>kuva kuwa 5 Ugushyingo 2019.  

= Amashuri yize =
Mimosa afite impamyabushobozi mu bijyanye no gucukumbura imigirire ya muntu,yatanzwe n' ikigo cya  ACI muri Australia mu  ishami ry’amashyirahamwe n’imari.   Yarangije kandi mu Ishuri ry’Ubuyobozi rya Maastricht, [[i Maastricht]],<ref>https://www.maastrichtuniversity.nl/</ref> mu [[Ubuholandi|Buholandi]], afite impamyabushobozi, mu bijyanye no gucunga imishinga.  

= Uburambe afite mukazi =
Mbere yo kugirwa Minisitiri w’imikino mu Rwanda, Mimosa yari Umuyobozi mukuru wa Sonarwa Life Company, ikigo cy’ubwishingizi bw' ibintu n'abantu i Kigali. Mbere yibyo, yari umuyobozi mukuru wa African Alliance Rwanda. African Alliance nitsinda ryamabanki yishoramari rikorera muri Afrika.  

= Inzobere mubyo gucunga umutungo =
Afite uburambe mubirebana namabanki burenga imyaka icumi cyane cyane mubikorwa byo gucunga umutungo, no mu bucuruzi mu bigendanye no kunguka. Yagize uruhare runini mu gushinga isosiyete ya mbere y’ubucuruzi bw’imigabane, ndetse n’ivunjisha rya mbere ry’ibicuruzwa byo muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba mu Rwanda.  

